reviews.text: Listen !!!! This is the best soul food you could possibly find in East New York/Brownsville area of Brooklyn, this food literally changed my life .food is always on point seasoned to perfection.
The food was delicious prepared probably I would recommend any to Aveah kitchenette
The customer service was 10/10, the owner explained the different kinds of meals to me and helped me picked the perfect meal. The food was the best thing!
The food is absolutely delicious, there is no picking one meal. You will want everything on the menu, the food is that good! Chef’s kiss! The own mannerisms is great! Very is friendly.

Aveah's Kitchenette, what can I say but five plus stars. I have been ordering food from her for months now,  and it is by far the best food in town. . I must tried everything on the menu and it just gets better and better.

If you don't try it your missing out!!
